comments.body:
[~agf2015] Due to adding material theme support, it is required now to target Android SDK 21 when building. This is set in the tiapp.xml using the following tag {{<uses-sdk android:targetSdkVersion="21"/>}}.

The error you are seeing is what you will see when targeting an Android SDK that is lower than 21(5.0). I would advise checking your tiapp.xml the above tag and correcting it to 21 if it is lower.
